# SecureVault — Fixes + Full Appearance System

## Root Causes Identified

| Issue | Root Cause | Fix |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Enterprise signs out | Session is in-memory only; any hard-nav or page reload clears it | Persist session to `sessionStorage` |
| Snake re-centers | `useEffect([dir])` restarts interval on every turn → resets snake | Use `useRef` for dir, single stable interval |
| Sidebar/footer overlap | Fixed `bottom-0` sidebar overlaps page footer | Hide footer on app-only routes |
| Dropdown opacity | `glass-nav` too transparent | Solid dark background for dropdown |
| Appearance settings don't work | Only visual toggles, no context applying changes | `AppearanceContext` writes to CSS vars + classes |

---

## Proposed Changes

### 1. [SessionContext.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/SessionContext.tsx) — Session Persistence
- On `setSession`: write to `sessionStorage` (secure tab-scoped, clears on tab close)
- On mount: restore from `sessionStorage`
- On [logout](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/SessionContext.tsx#29-33): clear `sessionStorage`

### 2. [profile/page.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/profile/page.tsx) — Snake Fix
- Move `dir` to `useRef` instead of `useState` — direction changes no longer restart the interval
- Single stable `useEffect([], [])` interval 
- Snake roams aimlessly forever (no length-reset), just bounces off walls with random direction

### 3. [layout.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/layout.tsx) — Hide Footer on App Routes
- Detect path via `usePathname` (in a new `FooterGuard` client component)
- Hide footer when path starts with `/dashboard`, `/settings`, `/profile`, `/messages`, `/audit-log`, `/vault-sharing`, `/profile`

### 4. [NavbarClient.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/NavbarClient.tsx) — Dropdown Opacity Fix
- Change dropdown background from `glass-nav` to a near-opaque dark panel

### 5. `AppearanceContext.tsx` [NEW] — Full Appearance System
Stores all settings, persisted to `localStorage`. Exposes:
- `bgStyle`: `"none" | "dots" | "grid" | "hex" | "circuit" | "matrix"`  
- `transitionStyle`: `"iris" | "shatter" | "portal"`  
- `successStyle`: `"handshake" | "decrypt" | "assemble"`  
- `glowIntensity`: 0–100 (CSS var override)  
- `motionLevel`: `"full" | "reduced" | "none"`  
- `fontStyle`: `"syne" | "inter" | "mono"`  
- `density`: `"compact" | "default" | "spacious"`  
- `borderRadius`: `"sharp" | "normal" | "round"`  

Applies changes instantly via `document.body.dataset.*` and CSS variables.

### 6. [VaultTransition.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/VaultTransition.tsx) — 3 Transition Styles
- **Iris** (current): glowing ring from click origin ← keep  
- **Shatter**: screen fractures into grid tiles that scatter  
- **Portal**: a swirling vortex/wormhole expands from center  
Reads `transitionStyle` from `AppearanceContext`.

### 7. [AuthSuccessAnimation.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/AuthSuccessAnimation.tsx) — 3 Success Styles  
- **Handshake** (current): hex rain → scanner → scramble text → ring ← keep  
- **Decrypt**: green matrix characters decode top-to-bottom revealing dashboard  
- **Assemble**: page content fragments fly in from different directions  
Reads `successStyle` from `AppearanceContext`.

### 8. [settings/page.tsx](file:///d:/Code%20Learning/WebP/SecretVault/securevault/frontend/src/app/settings/page.tsx) — Fully Wired Appearance Tab
Replaces the current Appearance tab with a comprehensive live-preview system:
- Each section has a **▶ Preview** button that opens a demo modal
- All toggles/selectors actually call `AppearanceContext` setters
- Live glow slider updates the CSS var in real time

### 9. `AppearanceDemo.tsx` [NEW] — Demo Modal
- A modal overlay (`z-[200]`) that demonstrates the selected option
- Background styles: shows the pattern in a miniaturized container  
- Transition styles: plays the transition animation in a contained box  
- Success styles: plays the auth success animation preview  

---

## Verification Plan

1. Navigate to Enterprise page while signed in — session should persist
2. Profile page — snake roams forever without resetting
3. Dashboard — sidebar doesn't overlap footer (footer hidden on app routes)
4. Dropdown opens over sidebar cleanly
5. Settings → Appearance → change bg style → body background updates live
6. Settings → Appearance → adjust glow slider → glow updates across the UI
7. Settings → Appearance → click Preview on each category → demo modal shows
8. Change transition style → vault iris/shatter/portal plays on next nav
9. All choices persist across page refresh (localStorage)
